    <item>
      <title>南非同意为 Transnet 提供 25 亿美元的一揽子支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/south-africa-will-provide-2-5-billion-guarantee-to-transnet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国家财政部同意向 Transnet SOC Ltd. 提供 470 亿兰特（25 亿美元）的一揽子支持计划，支持该国陷入困境的铁路和港口运营商改善财务和业绩的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/south-africa-will-provide-2-5-billion-guarantee-to-transnet</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 06:14:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金巨头和政策制定者对新世界大战的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2023-12-01/hedge-fund-managers-consider-world-war-a-growing-possibility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[相互关联的冲突的扩散引发了人们与过去的世界大战的比较——并使政策制定者集中精力采取措施防止冲突升级]]></description>
